| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1931 — Recovery Inhibition (chaos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 74a5aaf1-a8e4-5f80-9693-c60ae16c2ec3"
